芒聙聹(i) Verifying the authenticity of ownership documents;

芒聙聹(ii) Registering the interest of the closed bank on a specific property;

芒聙聹(iii) Consolidating ownership over an asset of the closed bank;

芒聙聹(iv) Securing certified true copies of documents held by the foregoing agencies/entities in relation to an asset of the closed bank;

芒聙聹(v) Securing the appropriate certification from the foregoing agencies/entities in relation to an asset of the closed bank; and

芒聙聹(vi) Performing other related activities;

芒聙聹(2) Conduct a physical or ocular inspection of the properties owned by, or mortgaged to, the closed bank, to determine their existence and present condition;

